metadata.name: PandaBlocks #1
metadata.description:
The Panda Blocks is a collection of 2048 NFT collectibles on the Ethereum blockchain. Each NFT is a unique combination of the fragments from submissions of artworks created by 23 renowned artists worldwide. The puzzle-like combinations can be 3x3, 2x2, and the rarest 1x1 that displays a single complete artwork.

This project is initiated by WeirDAO, in collaboration with Crypto Art Panda community. Visit [www.weirdao.io](https://www.weirdao.io) for more details and insights of upcoming projects, and follow us on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/Weir_DAO) to be updated with the latest news.
